    <h3>Tigers are the Best!</h3>
    <p>My interest in tigers came from the infamous feline villain from Walt Disney's "The Jungle Book," Shere Khan! Who also appeared in the spinoff Disney cartoon series "Tale Spin." His snarky overconfidence was something to enjoy.</p>
