        <p><h3>The Siberian tiger is awesome!</h3></p>
<p>The Siberian Tiger (Pictured Above) is my favorite breed of Tiger, though all tigers are pretty amazing creatures. Another reason I like the Tiger so much is because the standard black and orange color scheme is also my high school colors.</p>
